node.text:
This gamers incredible fortune saved them from way more than just a loss in a game. 😱

After buying a set of The Witcher Card Game, the gamer was on their way home when they were attacked by a stranger in an alleyway. After exchanging blows, the attacker fled, and upon finally getting home, AntonRauch looked in a mirror and immediately noticed a knife sticking out of their stomach. 

The knife had got stuck straight into the centre of the (thankfully) thick box, preventing it from reaching any skin. Poor Geralt on the front of the box didn't get away quite so easily though. Swipe to take a look 👉
